originalText.text: Sydney is an excellent Coach! She has helped me develop the confidence I need to transition in my career. Her warm and friendly demeanor immediately created a safe place for me to be vulnerable. I came to her feeling defeated and unhappy with where I was in life. She helped me identify limiting beliefs and fears that held me back. Her ability to ask the right questions, actively listen, and understand was very impressive. I have gained so much clarity and feel so empowered about my future. I believe that I can accomplish my goals and start anew. Sydney’s coaching has helped me make pivotal career decisions. I would recommend her to anyone looking to make a change in their career.
